        frameworks. I also have experience in backend development using various libraries.
      </p>
      <hr />
      <div class="mt-4 md:ml-8 md:mr-8">
        <RepoCard owner="vclemenzi" name="translatefox" desc="Translate you webpage on firefox" />
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hidden w-1/3 justify-end md:flex">
      <img src="https://skillicons.dev/icons?i=js" class="h-40 w-40" />
    </div>
  </div>
